 This package includes the check_mk agent for Linux systems.

Package: check-mk-agent-logwatch
Architecture: all
Depends: python, ucf (>= 0.8), check-mk-agent,
  ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: A general purpose Nagios-plugin for retrieving data
