Package: check-mk-multisite
Architecture: all
Depends: python, nagios3, ucf (>= 0.8), check-mk-livestatus,
  ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: apache2 | httpd
Description: A new and innovative GUI for viewing Nagios status information
 Check_MK introduces Multisite - a new and innovative GUI for viewing
 Nagios status information and controlling your monitoring system. It
 is based on MK Livestatus and aims at replacing the Nagios web GUI
 (also known as "the CGIs"). Multisite supports distributed monitoring
 in a very efficient way.

Package: check-mk-livestatus
Architecture: any
Depends: nagios3, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Provide immediate access to Nagios' status and log data
 The fastest and easiest way of accessing status and historic data.
 .
 This is used by check-mk-multisite.
